# Generated Reports

Markdown reports are generated here when running the levels:

```bash
python -m levels.level0_next_token    # → level0_next_token.md
python -m levels.level1_causal_attention  # → level1_causal_attention.md
python -m levels.level2_transformer_block # → level2_transformer_block.md
```

Reports contain the full execution trace: formula, inputs, outputs, shapes, and explanations for every operation.
